<html>
<head>
<link rel="StyleSheet" href="/style.css" type="text/css">
<title>Mustl test application - Configuration</title>
</head>
<body>

<font class="bigtitlebold">Configuration</font>
<br><font class="tiny">Settings will take effect only when the Save Settings button is pressed</font>

<form method="post" action="config.mhtml">
<input type="hidden" name="type" value="mustlonly">
<table width="100%" class="bgblue" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
<tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Command log</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustlcommandlog'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Command Log</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log all executed commands to stderr.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Net log</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustlnetlog'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Network Log</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log multiplayer game network activity to the network log.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Web log</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustlweblog'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Web Log</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log all access to the localweb server in the network log.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Verbose network log</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustlverboselog'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Verbose Network Log</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log additional information to network log.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Network traffic log</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustltrafficlog'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Network Traffic Log</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log all network traffic.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>

<td align="center" class="bglightblue">
 <font class="tinyblue">Log full IP address</font><br>
 <?mush mustlinputwrite('mustllogfullip'); ?>
</td>
<td>
 <font class="titlebold">Log Full IP Address</font>
 <br><font class="tiny">This option, when checked, will log full IP addresses and network names to network log, instead of the truncated form 127.0.x.x used to maintain privacy.</font>
</td>
</tr><tr>
<td align="center" class="bglightblue"><button name="update" value="Update" type="submit">Save Settings</button></td>
</tr>
</table>
</form>

</body>
</html>
